These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, spanish, german, canadian
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, october, august, february
4 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, snooker, go
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, gardening, cooking, fishing
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, emerald, apricot, purple
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
 2. the german is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 5. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the left of the person who likes emerald##8
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the left of the person who likes ebony##8
 9. the person who likes purple is the italian##1
10. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
11. the spanish is in an even position##4
12. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3
13. the person playing go is not to the right of the german##8
14. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the left of the person who likes purple##5
15. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
16. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Nationality    | canadian | spanish     | german     | italian |
| Birthday        | october  | november | august      | february      |
| Game         | go  | monopoly    | snooker | scrabble       |
| Hobby       | collecting | gardening   | cooking      | fishing  |
| Color   | emerald      | ebony  | apricot   | purple      |

